{"tid":662470,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"我呼吸系統差到極點","createTime":"2018-05-12T12:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T10:48:36.000Z","uid":129660,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"87198ea08cc1af56b1d63f48ebb3f0afc447bc4e","tid":662470,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:54:54.000Z","msg":"講緊唔係個肺, 而係呼吸系統既入口<br />\n平時盡量控制自己用鼻呼吸, 但發覺其實唔work<br />\n根本透唔夠氣, 長期處於半閉氣, 什至有D缺氧既狀態<br />\n試過好多方法: 切下鼻甲(切完好似仲衰), 洗鼻, 類固醇, 食敏感藥等等都無乜用<br />\n相反, mak大口呼吸係樣衰D, 但成個人會放鬆好多, 唔使咁用力<br />\n不過有時真係要Mak到好撚大先呼吸暢順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人, 指點下我可以做D咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faaab77674f6d84d39f6d989bc6ef7e40d019d37","tid":662470,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:56:15.000Z","msg":"mak大鼻哥窿透氣"},{"pid":"005e42282d1596b7bd176b73522f6a588bf84c31","tid":662470,"uid":129660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"faaab77674f6d84d39f6d989bc6ef7e40d019d37","tid":662470,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:56:15.000Z","msg":"mak大鼻哥窿透氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:59:21.000Z","msg":"個人覺得仲柒過MAK大口透氣"},{"pid":"3fbdf71af3c987aec19ce264101d610c379bf153","tid":662470,"uid":80958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T13:03:04.000Z","msg":"我個鼻長年都係塞七成 慣左用口透氣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f900a89ab8ef0153510cc9b1c70e78a4d7994e","tid":662470,"uid":136345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T13:22:57.000Z","msg":"係唔係因為無做運動既關係 因為我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f62a1310844f4b9761b84a4bad446fca43daed8","tid":662470,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8f900a89ab8ef0153510cc9b1c70e78a4d7994e","tid":662470,"uid":136345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy